@* THE DECOY. A real sibling component whose file name is exactly the name of SlotCard's fragment
   [Parameter]. It exists so the collision is real; the point of the witness is that it is NOT
   instantiated where the name is a slot -- and IS instantiated one level down, where it is a tag. *@
<p id="decoy">DECOY @ChildContent</p>

@code {
    [Parameter] public RenderFragment? ChildContent { get; set; }
}
